Attachments
precis:
Confirmation of a "SETTLEMENT AGREEMENT" between the Crown, the Province of
Ontario and THE MISSISSAUGA BAND which provides for the setting apart of
40,000 acres of land and the making of a compensatory payment in respect of
a claim pertaining to the 1852 survey of the northern boundary of the
Mississauga Reserve.
